headline: Elevance Health to Hold Conference Call and Webcast to Discuss Third Quarter 2025 Results on October 21
summary: INDIANAPOLIS, September 29, 2025--Elevance Health (NYSE: ELV) will release third quarter 2025 financial results on October 21, 2025, at 6:00 a.m. Eastern Daylight Time ("EDT"). Management will review these results and its outlook during a conference call at 8:30 a.m. EDT that same morning. headline: Beat the Market: 5 Dividend Stocks Chosen by Investing.com’s Warren AI
summary: Investing.com -- Dividend investors seeking both income and growth potential have compelling options in today’s market, according to Investing.com’s WarrenAI analysis. The AI-powered system has identified five standout dividend stocks across various sectors, combining attractive yields with significant upside potential based on fair value assessments, fundamentals, and technical indicators.

headline: What to Expect From Elevance Health’s Next Quarterly Earnings Report
summary: Elevance Health is slated to announce its fiscal third-quarter results next month, with analysts expecting earnings to fall in double digits, signaling headwinds for the company in the current market environment.
